    "The population of the study refers to the students studying in the level 1 and level 2 Bachelor programs of Business College, Prince Sattam bin Abdulaziz University, KSA.",
    "The respondents are all Arabic native speakers and learn English as a foreign language.",
    "English has been one of their compulsory subjects for 8-10 years.",
    "They are in their early twenties.",
    "They were chosen out of a population of about 2000 students."
